@Wismo.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5255

GET {{Wismo.Api_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###

POST {{Wismo.Api_HostAddress}}/api/webhooks/shopify/orders/create
Content-Type: application/json
X-Shopify-Shop-Domain: demo-store.myshopify.com
X-Shopify-Hmac-Sha256: <computed-base64-hmac>

{
  "id": 55123,
  "name": "#1001",
  "order_number": 1001,
  "email": "client@example.com",
  "created_at": "2026-03-10T09:45:00Z"
}

###

POST {{Wismo.Api_HostAddress}}/api/tickets/classify-preview
Authorization: Bearer <jwt>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerEmail": "",
  "messageBody": "Unde e pachetul meu? Comanda #ABC123, email ion.popescu@example.com"
}

###
